
/************************************************

  BDDs in CLP(BN)

A variable is represented by the N possible cases it can take

V = v(Va, Vb, Vc)

The generic formula is

V <- X, Y 

Va <- P*X1*Y1 + Q*X2*Y2 + ...


 
**************************************************/

